---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About - ARTANNA Luxury Home Decor"
  description="Learn about our commitment to bringing you the finest luxury home decor pieces."
>
  <div class="py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl text-center mb-16">About ARTANNA</h1>
      
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="prose prose-lg mx-auto">
          <p class="lead">Welcome to ARTANNA, where luxury meets home decor. We are passionate about curating exceptional pieces that transform living spaces into sophisticated sanctuaries.</p>
          
          <p>Our carefully selected collection represents the pinnacle of design and craftsmanship, bringing together contemporary elegance and timeless beauty.</p>
          
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl mt-12 mb-6">Our Story</h2>
          <p>Founded with a vision to make luxury accessible, ARTANNA has grown to become a trusted destination for discerning homeowners and interior designers alike.</p>
          
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl mt-12 mb-6">Our Promise</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li>
              <strong>Exceptional Quality</strong><br>
              Every piece in our collection meets our exacting standards for craftsmanship and design.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Expert Curation</strong><br>
              Our team carefully selects pieces that complement each other and your space.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Outstanding Service</strong><br>
              Personal attention and professional guidance throughout your journey.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Timely Delivery</strong><br>
              Secure and professional handling of your precious items.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>